  "detailed_description": "Storage Guys is a casual multiplayer co-op game where you and your friends take on the role of storage crew.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/c127eb9973b84e19e4b4c3b1ea1d7403.webp?t=1764959486\" width=450 height=50 /></span><br>Your job is to receive items at the input ports, sort and organize them in your warehouse, and ship them out through the correct output ports. Every successful shipment makes you money! Each item is labeled with an output region, so you’ll need to sort and ship them to the matching output ports. But watch out for expiration dates, you need to send items out before they expire!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/314185bc9983d781b02b2ee3230efa7b.poster.avif?t=1764959486\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/314185bc9983d781b02b2ee3230efa7b.webm?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/314185bc9983d781b02b2ee3230efa7b.mp4?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/6f3c61d904463de96b32a26f11934a43.webp?t=1764959486\" width=450 height=50 /></span><br>Manage a wide variety of incoming items, each with its own storage needs. Some require extra care, while others are easier to handle. Use specialized storage rooms called compounds to handle items with specific storing requirements, such as Freezer, Hazard, and UV compounds.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/a08eae610a0ea9c0f52a25d8b9816991.poster.avif?t=1764959486\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/a08eae610a0ea9c0f52a25d8b9816991.webm?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/a08eae610a0ea9c0f52a25d8b9816991.mp4?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/f674508e23737afcc16f256127640403.webp?t=1764959486\" width=450 height=50 /></span><br>Access the Shop through the Storage Terminal to purchase Shelves, Compounds, Equipment, and Decorations for your storage. As you earn money, you can expand your storage space, allowing you to grow your business and store more items. Customize your storage to enhance functionality and improve its look. Use different shelves, add compounds and equipment, and decorate to make your storage unique and attractive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/d5535264ebe62a0500cc59f53f7d4a41.poster.avif?t=1764959486\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/d5535264ebe62a0500cc59f53f7d4a41.webm?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/d5535264ebe62a0500cc59f53f7d4a41.mp4?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Storage Guys is a casual multiplayer co-op game where you and your friends take on the role of storage crew.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/c127eb9973b84e19e4b4c3b1ea1d7403.webp?t=1764959486\" width=450 height=50 /></span><br>Your job is to receive items at the input ports, sort and organize them in your warehouse, and ship them out through the correct output ports. Every successful shipment makes you money! Each item is labeled with an output region, so you’ll need to sort and ship them to the matching output ports. But watch out for expiration dates, you need to send items out before they expire!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/314185bc9983d781b02b2ee3230efa7b.poster.avif?t=1764959486\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/314185bc9983d781b02b2ee3230efa7b.webm?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/314185bc9983d781b02b2ee3230efa7b.mp4?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/6f3c61d904463de96b32a26f11934a43.webp?t=1764959486\" width=450 height=50 /></span><br>Manage a wide variety of incoming items, each with its own storage needs. Some require extra care, while others are easier to handle. Use specialized storage rooms called compounds to handle items with specific storing requirements, such as Freezer, Hazard, and UV compounds.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/a08eae610a0ea9c0f52a25d8b9816991.poster.avif?t=1764959486\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/a08eae610a0ea9c0f52a25d8b9816991.webm?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/a08eae610a0ea9c0f52a25d8b9816991.mp4?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/f674508e23737afcc16f256127640403.webp?t=1764959486\" width=450 height=50 /></span><br>Access the Shop through the Storage Terminal to purchase Shelves, Compounds, Equipment, and Decorations for your storage. As you earn money, you can expand your storage space, allowing you to grow your business and store more items. Customize your storage to enhance functionality and improve its look. Use different shelves, add compounds and equipment, and decorate to make your storage unique and attractive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/d5535264ebe62a0500cc59f53f7d4a41.poster.avif?t=1764959486\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/d5535264ebe62a0500cc59f53f7d4a41.webm?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103460/extras/d5535264ebe62a0500cc59f53f7d4a41.mp4?t=1764959486\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
